    "name": {
      "zh": "U.S Ordnance M60E6 7.62x51轻机枪（FDE）",
      "en": "U.S. Ordnance M60E6 7.62x51 light machine gun (FDE)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M60E6",
      "en": "M60E6"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 100,909₽ | 物品价值: 69,835 | Mechanic报价: 39,108₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 200,411₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < 1,867$ ≈ 224,040₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nM60E6是一款使用7.62x51口径弹药的轻机枪，是M60E4的轻量化改进款。M60曾因其硕大的尺寸和设计缺陷被称为“肥猪”。尽管存在各种缺陷，M60仍然被一些军队单位所使用。由U.S. Ordnance制造。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 100,909₽ | 物品价值: 69,835 | Mechanic报价: 39,108₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 200,411₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < 1,867$ ≈ 224,040₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nThe M60E6 is a 7.62x51 caliber light machine gun, a lightweight modification of the M60E4. The M60 was nicknamed \"The Pig\" due to its bulky size and design flaws. Despite its disadvantages, variants of the M60 are still used in some military units. Manufactured by U.S. Ordnance. Flat Dark Earth version."
    },
